<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>33</hymn_number>
<title>Dhambi Ikikulemea TZR33</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Dhambi ikikulemea,
 Kwa Bwana rehema;
 Hivi sasa tegemea
 Neno la salama.

[V2]
 Tegemea, tegemea,
 akwita sasa.
 Ni Mwokozi, ni
 Mwokozi; amini sasa.

[V3]
 Yesu amemwaga damu
 Ya nyingi baraka;
 Nawe sasa oga mumu
 Zioshwamo taka.

[V4]
 Ni njia yeye hakika
 Hwongoza rahani;
 Usikawe kumshika,
 Uwe barakani.

[V5]
 Karibu nawe wingie
 Mwetu safarini,
 Twende tukamwamkie,
 Milele Mbinguni.</lyrics>
</song>